Deluge is  a full-featured ​ BitTorrent  client for  Linux,  OS X,  Unix
and  Windows.  It uses ​libtorrent in its backend and  features multiple
user-interfaces including: GTK+, web and console.  The Deluge daemon is
able to run on headless machines with the user-interfaces being able to
connect remotely from any platform.  Deluge also features a rich plugin
collection; in fact, most of Deluge's functionality is available in the
form of plugins.

http://deluge-torrent.org/